From c1ea2f06841d60a6e4bc153620132d13df553720 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 15 Jul 2025 15:40:22 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Refactor monitor APIs to pass
 dp/dp_pdev instead of ar/ab

Currently for most of the monitor API's, ar/ab are passed as arguments.

Simplified monitor API signatures by using dp or dp_pdev as arguments.
ar and ab can be accessed via these structures when needed.

Patch-dependency:
	0404-0003-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-WCN7850-Status-Ring.patch
	0404-0004-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-WCN7850-Destination.patch
	0404-0005-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Move-QCN9274-ring-processing.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
